
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Bihar";
}

<link href="~/Script/StatesCss/bihar.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<div class="main-container">
    <!-- BACKGROUND IMAGE -->
    <div id="top-section-main">

        <div id="top-section-content">
            <h1> Vishwa Shanti Stupa, Vaishali </h1>
            <h2> Bihar </h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- PLACES TO VISIT SECTION -->
    <div id="feature-section">
        <h1 class="feature-section-title"> The top places to visit in <i>Bihar</i></h1>
        <div class="feature-content">
            <div class="cols-3">
                <img src="~/Image/StateImage/Bihar/bodh gaya.jpg">
                <h3> Bodh Gaya </h3>
                <p>  It is famous as it is the place where Gautama Buddha is said to have attained Enlightenment (Pali: bodhi) under what became known as the Bodhi Tree. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="cols-3">
                <img src="~/Image/StateImage/Bihar/rajgir.jpg">
                <h3> Rajgir </h3>
                <p> Rajgir is famous for its hot water springs, locally known as Brahmakund, a sacred place for Hindus where water from seven different springs (Saptarshi) merge and is notable for its healing effects.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cols-3">
                <img src="~/Image/StateImage/Bihar/patna.jpg">
                <h3> Patna </h3>
                <p> The Buddhist, Hindu and Jain pilgrimage centres of Vaishali, Rajgir, Nalanda, Bodh Gaya and Pawapuri are nearby and Patna City is a sacred city for Sikhs as the tenth Sikh Guru, Guru Gobind Singh was born here.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cols-3">
                <img src="~/Image/StateImage/Bihar/gaya.jpg">
                <h3> Gaya </h3>
                <p> Gaya is mostly known as the birthplace of Buddhism as Gautama Buddha attained nirvana in this holy site. Gaya has temples of great beauty and heritage and makes it one of the most desired spiritual destinations in India. </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- MAP SECTION -->
    <div id="showcase1-container">
        <div class="showcase">
            <div class="cols-2">
                <iframe class="showcase1-pic" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3675621.7635657713!2d83.5573414816727!3d25.886771580537744!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39ed5844f0bb6903%3A0x57ad3fed1bbae325!2sBihar!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1618240258482!5m2!1sen!2sin" width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="cols-2">
                <div class="feature-text">
                    <h1 class="section-title">
                        Facts of Bihar
                    </h1>
                    <p class="section-content">
                        <ul class="section-content-list">
                            <li>
                                The birthplace of Jainism and Buddhism.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Home to the oldest Hindu temple.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Was a significant centre during the Vedic period.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                The concept of non-violence originated from the land of Bihar.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Bihar is derived from the Sanskrit word.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- LAST SECTION -->
    <div id="call-to-action">
        <div class="showcase">
            <div class="cols-1">
                <h1 class="action-title">
                    What are you waiting for??
                </h1>
                <p style="line-height:1.2em;">
                    Book your tickets, pack your bags and
                    Get.. Set.. GO!!
                    If history was your favorite subject during school, then welcome to Bihar, it is waiting for you!!
                </p>
                <P>
                    <a href="#" class="BookHotelBtn"> BOOK A HOTEL TODAY!! </a>
                </P>
                <div class="text"> <p style="font-weight: 1000; font-style:italic;"> Gandhi Maidan - Patna </p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


